RudeServer NEWS - User visible changes.
See ChangeLog for more detailed information on internal changes
See the end for copying conditions.

__________________________________________________________________________________
Version 1.2

   ** Printing the Content-Type now includes the View's charset as well
	   Example:  Content-Type: text/html; charset=UTF-8

__________________________________________________________________________________
Version 1.1

	** It is now the responsibility of the View/Decorator in the webPlatform to
	   generate xsl:output tags and xsl:decimal-format tags.  Rudeserver is now
	   only ouputing the DTD and the outermost xsl:stylesheet tag....

